====================================================================
=========         SCoPE XML PLUG-IN README (v1.0.5)       ==========
====================================================================

This is a plug-in for SCoPE tool. This plug-in allows defining the 
platform through an XML file instead of creating it an the sc_main 
file.

SCoPE xml plug-in requires the following elements to be installed:
	- SCoPE v1.1.1 and all its requirements
	
To use the plug-in, compile your description following the examples.

The plug-in allows using the following options when executing the example:

        -xml file_name
        --xml-system-desription file_name     File with the platform and allocation information

        -xsc file_name
        --xml-system-configuration file_name  File with the system configuration parameters

        -xmd file_name
        --xml-metric_definition file_name     File with the definition of the metrics to be reported

        -xof file_name
        --xml-system-metrics file_name        File name for the output metric report
